  <brief_title>Effect of Local Anesthetic EMLA (Lidocaine 2.5% and Prilocaine 2.5%) Cream and Reduction in Dose, Pain and Intravenous Analgesic During Permanent Pacemaker Implantation</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
